                <p>There are a few Sonic the Hedgehog games on the SMS, like Sonic 1, 2, and Triple Trouble. As you saw earlier, one of the Sonic 2 unused sprites was a laughing sprite in the autodemo. For whatever reason, SEGA wanted that in there.</p>
<p>Another Sonic 2 oddity was Sonic tapping his foot when he's bored, instead of shrugging at the player. Tails was also, when you rescued him, supposed to yawn and rub his eyes while waiting.</p>
