<p>In Sonic Triple Trouble, Fang the Sniper had many different names. Fang the Sniper, Nack the Weasel, Nack the Wolf, and many others. Fang was also supposed to have an actual gun, not the popgun we see today.</p>
<figure class="post__image post__image--center" ><img loading="lazy" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/sonic/images/e/e1/Stt_TTBeta.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20101115095643" width="345" height="199" data-is-external-image="true">
<figcaption >Getting a little violent, aren't we?</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Sonic Chaos' Sonic had many color palette changes during development, as did Tails.</p>
